== Creating and uploading==
Users can enhance their VRChat experience by creating and uploading custom avatars, provided they comply with VRChat's [[Special:MyLanguage/Terms of Service|Terms of Service]]. To upload an avatar, users must first attain the [[Special:MyLanguage/Trust Rank|trust rank]] of "New User" and acquire the necessary tools, such as the recommended version of Unity and the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat SDK|VRChat SDK]].